{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081120/extras/runner-gif.gif?t=1729494139\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a world where technology has taken an unexpected turn, a robotic entity known as the Hound pursues human survivors. Gather up to 15 players for an exciting game of cat and mouse where roles can change in an instant! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Key Features: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Dynamic 1 vs Many Gameplay: One player starts randomly as the Hound, hunting down human survivors. As the game progresses, caught players join the Hound's team, creating an ever-evolving challenge. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Friend-filled Frights: Perfect for game nights, Hound: AUTOMATON offers a unique blend of horror and fun best enjoyed with friends. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Atmospheric Environments: From spooky abandoned warehouses to eerie cemetery grounds, each map is designed to keep you on your toes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Quick Rounds: Experience fast-paced matches lasting 5-7 minutes, ideal for multiple plays in a single game session. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Customizable Experience: Adjust settings to create the perfect balance of scares and laughs for your group. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Regular Updates: Look forward to future additions including new characters, levels, and game modes to keep the excitement fresh.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081120/extras/robots1-gif.gif?t=1729494139\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a variety of carefully crafted maps: \u2022 Warehouses with plenty of hiding spots among shipping containers \u2022 Misty cemeteries featuring old churches and shadowy graveyards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hound: AUTOMATON's attention to visual and audio detail creates an immersive experience. The moody lighting and atmospheric sound design enhance the thrill of the hunt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you're strategizing with fellow survivors or working together as hunters, Hound: AUTOMATON offers a unique party game experience that blends horror and hilarity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather your friends, turn down the lights, and prepare for a night of screams and laughter!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081120/extras/maps-gif.gif?t=1729494139\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"HUNT BEGINS","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3081120/b5c7bf1522b71766ba8de061e37b389994969b93.jpg"},{"name":"FIRST BLOOD","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3081120/ee396ce90e8039dbb5ff32d05e1f2c5f07b331c2.jpg"},{"name":"MASTER OF DISGUISE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3081120/0c3edd8aa03271d6c22183aeeb5a9adfbb3fd936.jpg"},{"name":"LAST ONE STANDING","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3081120/8a52450ec3715dbeb3bad1235d9da1cdb661f464.jpg"},{"name":"SPEED DEMON","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3081120/d2518c4786017332f15fb9280ab0ae05ca69ce63.jpg"},{"name":"HIDE AND SEEK CHAMPION","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3081120/6d17c7cdd9f9a66436502c2f238ef6fecf36b0bb.jpg"},{"name":"TERMINATOR","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3081120/a277e6bc7eeb7e9f4da99b846357603f52ec8057.j